      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait go to the er?? that seems like a lot for just a small cyst. i really dont want to deal with the wait and the cost. can i just put some antibiotic ointment on it and keep it covered for a day or two to see if it clears up myself? i have some neosporin in the cupboard",
